<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_118_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ıeber</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd gebetten habt von Nıkel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l3">Tenners ~ Des Poppenſteins vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> geſellen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe yecʒ bey eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l4"><expan>lıg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l5"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . Dem wır <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit eẅ <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒureden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l6">Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch . was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> von der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l7">mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> . / daʒ Jr Jm das <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l8">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_118" id="58r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufsess, ritter </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns aber
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und gebetten habt von Nikel
                        Tenners, des Poppensteins und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> gesellen
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die yecz bey ewch
                                <expan>lig<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> von der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
                        sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
